Darkwind supports Giphy integration on supported channels and in the web
client.

If a channel supports it, placing a semicolon before your phrase shares
a GIF along with your normal text line.

Example:

  gossip ;hell yeah brother

Useful commands:

  giphy on
  giphy off
  giphy status
  testgiphy <search phrase>

The giphy command controls whether the popup window appears for you. It
does not suppress the normal text line in the channel.

testgiphy previews a search only for you so you can try phrases without
posting them publicly.

See also: help giphy
